race.description: Ruc Turner Bowls Club Country Boosted Mdn Hcp
race.comment: SHEZAIN (3) returns from a lengthy break. Even run on debut when third in the Black Opal Preview over 1000m at Canberra 22 months ago. Ran fourth in her only trial over 800m at Goulburn and senior rider booked. REVEILLON (7) has slick gate speed but can't draw a decent gate. Knocked up late at her second run back when eighth over 1300m at this track. Worth another chance in this easier race. SPLENDID MAGNUS (11) first start for the Jarvis yard and resumes after failing to fire in two career starts in Victoria. Back without a trial and blinkers go on from the inside gate. Keep safe. DUBBO BOY (4) showed ability in his first prep, before disappointing at his first run back when a fading seventh over 1100m at Nowra. No surprise to see him run a better race today.
